===Arms===
In 1858, Louise and the three younger of her sisters were granted use of the [[Royal coat of arms of the United Kingdom|royal arms]], with an [[inescutcheon]] of the [[Coat of arms of Saxony|shield of Saxony]] and differenced by a [[Label (heraldry)|label]] of three points [[argent]]. On Louise's arms, the outer points bore cantons [[gules]], and the centre a rose gules. In 1917, the inescutcheon was dropped by royal warrant from [[George V of the United Kingdom|George V]].<ref>{{cite web|first=Francois R.|last=Velde|url=http://www.heraldica.org/topics/britain/cadency.htm|title=Heraldica – British Royalty Cadency|publisher=Heraldica.org|accessdate=20 August 2011}}</ref>

